description.narrative: Scholarships are offered to citizens of 112 countries to undertake tertiary study and short term training in New Zealand and, for Pacific citizens, in the Pacific region. The primary geographic focus of the New Zealand Scholarships Programme is the Pacific and ASEAN regions. Priority themes and sectors are agreed with the partner country or region.
